review.reviewBody:
I made it healthier, it was good! Ill adjust more next time. 
 1) Left out the 2nd can of soup , used Sour cream &amp; greek yogurt (Id use cream cheese but I was out--I suggest it ) added powdered mustard, garlic powder, salt. 
 2) left out almost 1/4 of the noodles; 
 3) Skipped processed cheese, used some shredded mozzarella &amp; parm.
 (next time Cheddar ); 
4) Used frozen peas AND carrots- more nutritious, less carbs . And yes, the cream cheese Ill use next time, and Ill likely add mayo too arent health foods but they're purer. To each his own.
